title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Dec 27 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Dec 27 2021
description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 3:

EIB Guest Host Michael Berry, from NewsRadio 740 KTRH in Houston, takes your calls on what you saw happening on January 6th. Arrogant Joe Scarborough is sick of comparisons between the endless Antifa and BLM riots to the mostly peaceful protest at the Capitol. Think what it means to tell Marines: Get this jab or you're out. Navy SEAL Marcus Luttrell, author of Lone Survivor, pays tribute to Frogman Richard Marcinko, Founding Commander of SEAL Team Six.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
